security: harden .gitignore for secrets and AI tool safetyclaude-code.log

# Cloud & Infrastructure
.terraform/
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backupUpdates .gitignore with comprehensive security rules:
- Explicitly blocks .env, auth.json, key.json, and secrets.json
- Adds patterns for Claude Code CLI (.claudecode/, claudecode.json, claudecode.log)
- Excludes large ML artifacts and dataset directories
- Adds infrastructure-specific exclusions (GCP/Terraform)
- Protects local environment files like .afrilion_env

This ensures that the project remains safe while using Claude Code CLI
in parallel with the TPU environment.
